<section id="story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <div class="slider single-item">
            <div class="text_background"> <p> <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> and <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> first met years ago through mutual friends. After meeting several times they realized they had many things in common, such as a fondness for Dwight Yoakam songs.
            <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> decided to ask <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> on a date. He was nervous, but determined.</div>
            <div><%= image_tag("story/firstdate.jpg", class: "comsize") %></div>
            <div class="text_background"> <p> That weekend they watched X-Men: First Class and ate California tart frozen yogurt at Fro-Jo's. They sat on a blanket under the stars and shared stories.

            For one reason or another <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> and <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> drifted. However, it was clear there was something between them.

            A couple of months later some of their friends planned a trip to a corn maze and invited <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> and <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> along. They had a great time. That night they carved pumpkins together.

            Once more <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> asked <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> on a date.</div>
            <div><%= image_tag("story/secondfirstdate.jpg", class: "comsize") %></div>
            <div class="text_background"> <p> <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> and <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> went on many more dates and spent countless hours together. Soon it was <font color= "Cranberry">LOVE </font>. The two went on camping trips, visited new places, played video games, and watched lots of TV shows.

            One day <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> and <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> were sitting in the living room with <font color= "Purple">Artemus </font>.</div>
            <div><%= image_tag("story/artemuspredictsthefuture.jpg", class: "comsize") %></div>
            <div class="text_background"> <p> After that things became more serious.Sometime later <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> and <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> took a trip to Boston. The day before they left for home <font color= "Coral">Todd </font> took <font color= "Teal">Kristen </font> on a walk through a beautiful Boston park.</div>
            <div><%= image_tag("story/theproposal.jpg", class: "comsize") %></div>
            <div class="text_background"> <p> And they are still having adventures.</div>
          </div> 
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

